title.en: coco: The data model for Coconut Knowledge Graph

author: Edgard Marx, Stefan Schmidt-Dichte, Istvan J. Mocsy

description.en: The Coconut Ontology contains the data model of Coconut Knowledge Graph. It facilitates the knowledge graph data manipulation and consumption through concepts such as natural products, molecules, and their respective properties.
